<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>FAQ | JellyMart</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/theme.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('navbar') %>

  <div class="container my-5" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <div class="section-title mb-3">
      <span>Frequently Asked Questions</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-muted mb-4">Quick answers to common questions about shopping, delivery, and payments.</p>

    <div class="layout-card mb-3">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Orders and Checkout</h4>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>How do I place an order?</strong><br>Browse products, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout to choose delivery and payment.</p>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Can I edit quantities in my cart?</strong><br>Yes. You can update quantities from the cart page and your totals will update automatically.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-card mb-3">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Delivery and Self-Pickup</h4>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>Delivery</strong><br>Select Delivery and enter your address. A $4 delivery fee applies.</p>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Self-Pickup</strong><br>Select Self-Pickup to collect at postal code 320115. Daily 10:00â€“20:00. Bring your order ID for verification.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-card mb-3">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Payment Methods</h4>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>What payment methods are available?</strong><br>PayPal, NETS QR, and Stripe (card) are supported.</p>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>How does NETS QR work?</strong><br>A QR code is generated for your order. Scan it with your banking app to complete payment.</p>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Why is a payment method unavailable?</strong><br>In sandbox mode, some providers require extra setup. Contact support if a method fails consistently.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-card mb-3">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Order Confirmation and Invoice</h4>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>Where can I find my invoice?</strong><br>After payment, you'll be redirected to your invoice. You can also view past orders under My Purchases.</p>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Can I print my invoice?</strong><br>Yes. Use the Print button on the invoice page.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-card mb-3">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Cancellations and Returns</h4>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Can I cancel or return an order?</strong><br>No. All sales are final and we do not accept cancellations or returns.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="layout-card">
      <h4 class="mb-2">Common Issues</h4>
      <p class="mb-2"><strong>Payment failed</strong><br>Please retry with another method or confirm your payment provider settings.</p>
      <p class="mb-0"><strong>Order not appearing</strong><br>Refresh the page or check My Purchases. If it still doesn't appear, contact support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
